room_title: Escape room "The Search for Leviathan" by Enter the Imaginarium in Pittsburgh
room_description: Far beneath the abysmal seawaters lurk ancient secrets and buried treasures, where shadowy creatures lie dormant in their primal sleep, and sunken mariners fall further from mortal ports. Here you and your crew will decipher maps and chart a course to navigate the mysteries of the treacherous deep on a nautical adventure in search of Leviathan.
